                                "byte_start": 0,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Justice Breyer has the opinion of the Court in two cases this morning as well."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 4.851,
                        "stop": 299.232,
                        "byte_start": 0,
